                    <%= message %>
                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>

        <tr>
            <td>
                <p>
                    I’ll review this and reply within <span style="color:#ffcc00 ;font-size: larger;font-weight: bold;">
                        in
                        2 business day </span>
                    If your request is urgent, please reply directly to this email or use this link:

                </p>
            </td>
        </tr>
       <tr>
            <td>
                <a href="mailto:MagnetsDev@gmail.com"
                    style="display: inline-block; text-transform: capitalize; background-color: #ffcc00; font-weight: bold; border-radius: 16px; padding: 15px 20px; color:#2a2d36; text-decoration: none;">
                    Reply / Follow up
                </a>
            </td>
        </tr>


    </table>
